snippet.title: Sonic 2 - Pink Edition | Walkthrough
snippet.description: Sonic 2 - Pink Edition is a character swap hack. We can play as Amy Rose and Cream in Sonic the hedgehog 2. Emerald hill Zone walkthrough.
